@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@adminKey = your_optional_admin_key_here

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List cases
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cases

### Get one case
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cases/case-1

### Create session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caseId": "case-1",
  "learnerName": "Frontend Demo User"
}

### Send learner message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_ID/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "How long have you had the fever and cough?"
}

### The response includes a provider field
### "gemini" when GEMINI_API_KEY is set
### "local-scripted" otherwise

### Evaluate learner submission
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_ID/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "diagnosis": "Community acquired pneumonia",
  "reasoning": "Fever, productive cough, pleuritic chest pain, and worsening shortness of breath make pneumonia likely."
}

### Admin analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/analytics
x-admin-key: {{adminKey}}

### Admin sessions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/sessions?limit=20
x-admin-key: {{adminKey}}
